          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1636392606605-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut them into thick strips</p><p>Peel and roughly slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and<strong> sliced onion</strong> to a separate baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until the veg is soft and tender – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1636392611101-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1636392611101-x400.jpg",
